  "description": "The chaos engine at its most domesticated. Lorenz topology at chaosIndex 0.02 — near-periodic, just barely alive. The leash holds firm at 0.95, binding the butterfly to its pitch. Heavy damping at 0.85 suppresses harmonic spray. The result is not chaos — it is the memory of chaos, made safe for the room. A strange attractor reading to children at bedtime.",
